headline: Wall Street Has a Mixed Opinion on EOG Resources (EOG), Here’s Why
summary: ​EOG Resources, Inc. (NYSE:EOG) is one of the Best Very Cheap Stocks to Invest In. On November 20, Devin McDermott from Morgan Stanley maintained a Hold rating on the stock, raising the price target from $136 to $138.
